Activities.description: List of invoice activities. Invoice audit log

ClonedFromId.description: Indicate from which invoice this invoice has been cloned from

DiscountAmount.description: Amount that goes as a discount

Duedate.description: Indicates when the invoice will be proclamed as due

EnablePartialPayments.description: Indicate that the invoice allows the user to pay the invoice partially

InvoiceCategoryId.description: Hold the id of the invoice category

IssuedOn.description: Indicates when the invoice was issued

PaymentGateways.description: List of enabled payment gateways for this invoice

PoNumber.description: Unique number generated by the buyer

RecurringProfileId.description: Hold the id of the recurring profile

ShouldSendReminders.description: Should send email reminders to client?

Status.description: Indicate the status of the invoice (paid/unpaid/overdue)

SubTotalAmount.description: Total amount of the invoice without tax

TaxAmount.description: Amount that goes to the tax

TotalAmount.description: Total amount of the invoice with tax
